nQueued.description: # of data blocks queued for this dive

nTries.description: # of tries to get the data block receive status

parXstat.description: parse_x_reply status in the last surface session

SBDIstat.description: ATSBD return status in last surface session

SBDsecs.description: time taken in sending last SBD message

Vple.description: pump battery voltage at end of last pump

vac0.description: pcase vacuum before filling oil bladder at surface

vac1.description: pcase vacuum after filling oil bladder at surface

PumpT_Hi.description: total time pumped out, up to the last surface pump

SPRX.description: Surface pressure before reset offset (previous dive)

SPRXL.description: Surface pressure after reset offset (previous dive)

diagP0.description: Pressure scan at start of ascent

diagT0.description: Temperature scan at start of ascent

diagS0.description: Salinity scan at start of ascent

DPavg0.description: Average pressure over 1st half of drift

DTavg0.description: Average temperature over 1st half of drift

DSavg0.description: Average salinity over 1st half of drift

DPavg1.description: Average pressure over 2nd half of drift

DTavg1.description: Average temperature over 2nd half of drift

DSavg1.description: Average salinity over 2nd half of drift

ventTm.description: time that air vent motor ran

ventStat.description: LLD status before and after the air vent ran

nSent.description: # of Iridium messages sent during the last surfacing

phBat0.description: pH bias voltage right after turning off (end of surface)

phBat1.description: pH bias voltage right before turning off (mid-drift)
